299
00:27:24,660 --> 00:27:28,920
<i>Your Majesty, long time no see.</i>

300
00:27:29,840 --> 00:27:31,720
Immortal Lord?

301
00:27:35,060 --> 00:27:39,280
<i>A part of my spirituality rests on your GO piece.</i>

302
00:27:39,300 --> 00:27:44,020
<i>Through it, I can connect with your heart and communicate telepathically with you.</i>

303
00:27:44,020 --> 00:27:45,880
