304
00:27:46,360 --> 00:27:49,800
<i>In the Divine-Devil War, I was in charge of the rear</i>

305
00:27:49,800 --> 00:27:54,180
<i> and allocated divine tools and immortal beasts to the immortals.</i>

306
00:27:54,180 --> 00:28:00,760
<i>On the eve of the war, His Supreme Majesty entrusted me to protect you if the war intensified.</i>

307
00:28:00,760 --> 00:28:03,880
<i>However, I was at the rear and you were on the front line.</i>

308
00:28:03,880 --> 00:28:05,920
<i>Worried that I wouldn't be able to take care of you,</i>

309
00:28:05,920 --> 00:28:11,980
