310
00:28:11,980 --> 00:28:17,200
<i>After so many years, I didn't expect to meet you here.</i>

311
00:28:18,000 --> 00:28:23,440
<i>If His Supreme Majesty really is that mysterious person, why would he save me and then try to kill me?</i>

312
00:28:26,160 --> 00:28:31,420
