316
00:28:50,860 --> 00:28:53,640
<i>The Devils forced me into a hopeless situation.</i>

317
00:28:53,640 --> 00:28:58,900
<i>I fought the devil soldiers up front, but one of them attacked from behind.</i>

318
00:28:58,900 --> 00:29:03,440
<i>Caught off guard, I tried to see who it was.</i>

319
00:29:06,580 --> 00:29:11,520
<i>I looked up... and saw my face.</i>

320
00:29:18,500 --> 00:29:22,100
<i>I understood immediately that this person could use the Puppet Spell </i>

321
00:29:22,100 --> 00:29:26,260
<i>to pretend to be someone else and hide his identity.</i>

322
00:29:32,740 --> 00:29:36,600
<i>I couldn't expose him in the end.</i>

323
00:29:36,600 --> 00:29:40,720
What happened that year was due to my oversight.

324
00:29:40,720 --> 00:29:43,940
To prove your innocence to the Heavenly Realm,

325
00:29:43,940 --> 00:29:52,640
we have to ask your consent for us to open the coffin and find the evidence to avenge you.

326
00:29:52,640 --> 00:30:00,740
<i>This man plotted to kill celestial deities, absorb three emperors' divine power, and then quietly escape.</i>

327
00:30:00,740 --> 00:30:03,900
<i>He has fathomless immortal power and is very cunning.</i>

328
00:30:03,900 --> 00:30:05,320
<i>Others are no match for him.</i>

329
00:30:05,320 --> 00:30:09,440
<i>If you continue to pursue this, you'll put your life in danger.</i>

330
00:30:09,440 --> 00:30:15,120
